Since 2011, Global Citizen says it has recorded more than 19 million "actions" from its followers, driving a different set of goals.
It states that these actions helped spur world leaders to announce commitments and policies equivalent to more than $37 billion set to impact the lives of more than 2,250,000,000 people by 2030.
